itunes:summary:
Ross Patterson and Dan Hollaway sit down with one of the most entertaining men in Congress, Matt Gaetz, the Republican out of Florida as they discuss why old people should be run out politics, why he's leading the charge for the new Republican party, how Trump will win big in the upcoming election, and his new book "Firebrand: Dispatches From The MAGA Revolution."  Also, Ross and Dan break down the Breonna Taylor verdict that happened live on air and what it means for the people of Louisville.
